                Victoriam <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustam</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Fabius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Fabullus testamento fieri <lb n="3"/>ponique iussit ex HS <expan><abbr>IIII</abbr><ex>quattuor milibus</ex></expan> huic dono <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Fabius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Fabianus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>her</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> XX non deduxit et <expan><abbr>atmod</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>HS <expan><abbr>VI</abbr><ex>sex milibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicavit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite 2 Dübellöcher zur Befestigung der Statue. Das Stück ist nicht mehr auffindbar.</p>
